section#sponsors
  .container
    h2.section-header
      ' Sponsors
      .line
    .row
      .col-sm-12.text-center
        p RedDotRubyConf could not have become such a diverse and vibrant event, without our friendly community and our generous sponsors and supporters.
        p If you'd like to support and engage our Ruby community, please take a look at our #{link_to 'Sponsor Kit', asset_path('rdrc2017_sponsorkit.pdf'), target: "_blank"} and #{mail_to 'organisers@reddotrubyconf.com', 'get in touch with us', subject: "Sponsorship Enquiry for RedDotRubyConf 2017", target: "_blank"} for more information. Thank you!

    .row.text-center
      .col-sm-12.text-center
        h3.section-header
          ' Gold
          .line
      .col-sm-12.col-sm-offset-3
        .col-sm-6
          .sponsor
            = link_to 'https://hired.com.sg/', target: "_blank" do
              = image_tag 'sponsors/hired.jpg'

    .row.text-center
      .col-sm-12.text-center
        h3.section-header
          ' Supporting Sponsors
          .line
      .col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-4
